  "body": "# Bug Report\r\n\r\n## Description\r\n\r\nThe notification counter doesn't reset to zero after I check what it is notifying about.\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2023-11-15 11-32-47](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/7126627/df67d970-6f25-4cb9-a510-3939c0f5159f)\r\n\r\n## Steps to reproduce\r\n\r\n1. Send a request to join a community.\r\n2. Get accepted to that community.\r\n3. Click the notification in the upper right corner.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n\r\nThe notification counter resets to zero.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n\r\nThe notification counter shows a non-zero value (in gray if that's important).\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n\r\n- Status desktop version: Current version 0.9.90, Status Go version 0.171.12\r\n- Operating System: Ubuntu 20.04.6 LTS\r\n\r\n",
